---

## What Works

- All 9 MCP tools register and expose correct schemas
- `agent_instructions` prompt is well-formed and useful
- FastAPI backend routes and CORS are correct
- Frontend pages wired correctly in `App.tsx` (9 routes)
- `OpencodeClient` HTTP layer is clean — correct async httpx usage, graceful error paths
- Dependency stack is current (fastmcp 3.2.4, fastapi 0.136.1, starlette 1.0.0, pydantic 2.13.3)
